  "description": "A high-tech refrigerator with a spectacular black body. This model is equipped with a wide range of innovative technologies, which allows you to store products in the most suitable conditions for this. The cooling system uses the dynamic principle of operation. Thanks to AdaptTech technology, the power unit is able to regulate the load on the circulation circuit, depending on the characteristics of the operation of the working chambers. The Gorenje NRK 620 EABXL4 refrigerator received 3D forced ventilation. This is a high-performance cooling system with Multiflow 360 multi-flow distribution. With this technology, cold is supplied to each shelf and section separately. An interesting feature of the model is the presence of a container with regulation of both humidity and temperature. This box can be made into a freshness zone or a moisture zone, depending on the products that need to be stored. To control the operating modes of the refrigerator, a touch panel with a screen is used. The rich black colour of the case makes the refrigerator even more prestigious. This is a spectacular-looking model that will make the kitchen look professional. The wide functionality of the refrigeration device will provide the products with the best storage conditions.",
